'''''Skeleton Coast''''' ni filime y’intambara y’abacanshuro yo muri 1987 yakozwe na John Cardos muri firime eshatu za mbere kuri producer Harry Alan Towers . Nibwo bwambere muri Towers 'Breton Film Productions<ref>Namibia's Skeleton Coast: Explore the 'end of the Earth' - CNN <nowiki>https://edition.cnn.com</nowiki> › article › skeleton-coast-namibia</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Mugihe cy'intambara yo muri [[Angola]] umukozi wa CIA Michael Smith akorana ninyeshyamba za UNITA<ref>How to watch and stream Skeleton Coast - 1988 on Roku <nowiki>https://www.roku.com</nowiki> › What's On › Movies</ref>. Yafashwe n’ingabo za [[Angola]], yoherezwa muri gereza kugira ngo abazwe n’umudage w’iburasirazuba witwa Major Schneider<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) — The Movie Database (TMDB) <nowiki>https://www.themoviedb.org</nowiki> › movie › 81351-skeleton...</ref>. Se wa Smith, Koloneli Bill Smith wahoze mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru Colonel Bill Smith ntabwo yizera leta ya [[Amerika]] kurekura umuhungu we<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › skeleton-coast</ref>. Koloneli yagiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo y'uburengerazuba]] aho yishyuye Elia amayobera kugirango amenye amakuru yukuri kubyerekeye umuhungu we aho yari ari imbohe<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) Full Movie | M4uHD <nowiki>https://m4uhd.tv</nowiki> › watch-movie-skeleton-coast-1988-1...</ref>. Colonel Smith aha akazi abacanshuro barindwi azajyana muri [[Angola]] gutabara umuhungu we<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) - MCU Times <nowiki>https://mcutimes.com</nowiki> › Movies › titles › skeleton-coast</ref>.

Kapiteni Simpson, umuyobozi w’inzego zishinzwe umutekano z’ikirombe cya diyama afite umugabo uhanze amaso Coloneli atinya ko ashobora kuba akora magendu ya diyama<ref>Casting de Skeleton Coast (1988) - SensCritique <nowiki>https://www.senscritique.com</nowiki> › details</ref>. Umugore wa Elia, Opal akomeje kugirana umubano utemewe na Simpson amumenyesha ko Coloneli yishe umuntu w’umutekano we<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) on Sheer Entertainment (United ... <nowiki>http://www.videocollector.co.uk</nowiki> › skeleton-coast</ref>, mu byukuri yishwe na Rick Weston, umuyobozi w’ingabo bwite za Smith<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) movie posters - CineMaterial <nowiki>https://www.cinematerial.com</nowiki> › movies › skeleton-coast...</ref>. Rick yamenyesheje Coloneli ko yari umukozi wibanga wa [[Angola]]. Elia yahise amenya ko Col. Smith yamwishyuye amafaranag yamiganano<ref>Skeleton Coast (1988) - Comeuppance Reviews <nowiki>http://www.comeuppancereviews.net</nowiki> › 2012/03 › skelet...</ref>. Binjiye muri Angola, abacanshuro bafatanya na Sekassi, umuyobozi wo mu bwoko bwa Jonas Savimbi w’inyeshyamba kugira ngo bashyigikire gutabara Michael Smith<ref>Angola Civil War - Action [Large Box] Oliver Reed - VHS <nowiki>https://www.goldenclassmovies.com</nowiki> › products › skelet...</ref>.

